title: 107_hr4532
content: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 2007, the duty on Disperse Orange 30, Disperse Blue 79:1, Disperse Red 167:1, Disperse Yellow 64, Disperse Red 60, Disperse Blue 60, Disperse Blue 77, Disperse Yellow 42, Disperse Red 86, and Disperse Red 86:1.
